<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="WordRace is a free real-time multiplayer word puzzle game. Race your friends to guess the 5-letter word before they do. No download needed." />
  <title>WordRace ⚡ – Real-Time Multiplayer Word Battle</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --green: #4ade80;
      --green-glow: #4ade8055;
      --yellow: #fbbf24;
      --gray: #3f3f46;
      --dark: #09090b;
      --card: #0f1010;
      --border: #1c1c1e;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: var(--dark);
      color: #e4e4e7;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background: #09090bcc;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ffffff0d;
    }
    .nav-brand {
      font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: var(--green);
    }
    .nav-brand span { color: #fff; }
    .nav-links a { color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-left: 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 7rem 2rem 4rem;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 60%, #4ade8014 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 80% 20%, #fbbf2408 0%, transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
      background: #4ade8012; color: var(--green);
      border: 1px solid #4ade8030;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .hero h1 .accent {
      color: transparent;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--green);
      text-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--green-glow);
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
      color: #3a5c3a;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 1rem; color: #52525b;
      max-width: 520px; line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    /* ── Tile demo ── */
    .tile-demo {
      display: flex; gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .tile {
      width: 52px; height: 52px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 900; color: #fff;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }
    .tile.green { background: #16a34a; }
    .tile.yellow { background: #b45309; }
    .tile.gray   { background: #3f3f46; }

    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: var(--green); color: #000;
      font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.95rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem; border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 0 28px var(--green-glow);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--green-glow); }

    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: transparent; color: #888;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem; border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #1c1c1e; text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: #fff; }

    /* ── How it works ── */
    .how {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .section-label { text-align: center; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .section-title { text-align: center; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 800; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .section-desc { text-align: center; color: #3f3f46; font-size: 0.95rem; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; line-height: 1.6; }

    .steps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .step-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: #4ade8015; border: 1px solid #4ade8030;
      color: var(--green); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    }
    .step-card h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e4e4e7; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .step-card p  { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #52525b; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ── Color guide ── */
    .colors {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      background: #0c0c0e;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .color-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .color-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.5rem;
      display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;
    }
    .color-swatch {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: #fff;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .color-card h4 { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: #d4d4d8; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
    .color-card p  { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #52525b; line-height: 1.4; }

    /* ── Power-ups ── */
    .powerups {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }
    .powerup-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .powerup-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .powerup-card:hover { border-color: #4ade8033; }
    .powerup-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .powerup-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e4e4e7; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; }
    .powerup-card p  { font-size: 0.83rem; color: #52525b; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ── Modes ── */
    .modes {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
      background: #0c0c0e;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .modes-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .mode-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .mode-card:hover { border-color: #4ade8033; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .mode-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .mode-card h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e4e4e7; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .mode-card p  { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #52525b; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta {
      text-align: center; padding: 6rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 100%, #4ade8008 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cta h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 900; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .cta p { color: #3f3f46; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-url { color: #4ade80; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; font-family: monospace; }

    footer {
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.78rem; color: #27272a;
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    footer a { color: #3f3f46; text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: #aaa; }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <span class="nav-brand">Word<span>Race</span> ⚡</span>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#how">How to Play</a>
      <a href="#modes">Modes</a>
      <a href="#play">Play Now</a>
      <a href="../">Developer</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ── Hero ── -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">⚡ Real-Time Multiplayer</div>
    <h1>WORD<br><span class="accent">RACE</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Multiplayer Word Battle</p>
    <p class="hero-desc">Race your friends to guess the 5-letter word in real-time. Use power-ups, outsmart your opponent, and become the fastest mind.</p>

    <div class="tile-demo">
      <div class="tile green">W</div>
      <div class="tile yellow">O</div>
      <div class="tile gray">R</div>
      <div class="tile green">L</div>
      <div class="tile green">D</div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-btns" id="play">
      <a href="https://wordrace-game.netlify.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">⚡ &nbsp;Play Free Now</a>
      <a href="#how" class="btn-secondary">How to Play →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── How it works ── -->
  <section class="how" id="how">
    <p class="section-label">How to Play</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Simple to Learn, Hard to Win</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Both players race to crack the same 5-letter word. Guess smart, use power-ups, win 3 rounds first.</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <h3>Share a Link</h3>
        <p>No download, no account needed. Create a room and send the link to your opponent.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <h3>Guess the Word</h3>
        <p>Both players see the same mystery word. Type guesses and use tile colors to narrow it down.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <h3>Use Power-Ups</h3>
        <p>Peek reveals a hidden letter. Sabotage freezes your opponent's keyboard for 5 seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <h3>Win the Series</h3>
        <p>First to win 3 rounds takes the match. Earn XP and rank up from Bronze to Legend.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Tile color guide ── -->
  <section class="colors">
    <p class="section-label">Tile Colors</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Read the Board</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Every guess gives you clues. Learn to read them fast.</p>

    <div class="color-cards">
      <div class="color-card">
        <div class="color-swatch" style="background:#16a34a;">A</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Green</h4>
          <p>Right letter, right spot. Lock it in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="color-card">
        <div class="color-swatch" style="background:#b45309;">A</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Yellow</h4>
          <p>Right letter, wrong spot. Move it around.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="color-card">
        <div class="color-swatch" style="background:#3f3f46;">A</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Gray</h4>
          <p>Letter not in the word. Eliminate it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Power-ups ── -->
  <section class="powerups">
    <p class="section-label">Power-Ups</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Turn the Tables</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">One power-up can change the entire round. Use them wisely.</p>

    <div class="powerup-grid">
      <div class="powerup-card">
        <div class="powerup-icon">🔍</div>
        <h3>Peek</h3>
        <p>Reveals a mystery letter in the hidden word for free. One use per game — save it for when you're stuck.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="powerup-card">
        <div class="powerup-icon">💣</div>
        <h3>Sabotage</h3>
        <p>Freezes your opponent's keyboard for 5 full seconds. Just enough time to pull ahead and guess the word first.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Modes ── -->
  <section class="modes" id="modes">
    <p class="section-label">Game Modes</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Play Your Way</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">VS friends or go solo — there's a mode for every mood.</p>

    <div class="modes-grid">
      <div class="mode-card">
        <div class="mode-icon">⚔️</div>
        <h3>VS Mode</h3>
        <p>Head-to-head best-of-5 series. First to win 3 rounds takes the match. Real-time, real pressure.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-card">
        <div class="mode-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>Quick Play</h3>
        <p>Solo timed sprint. New word every game. Race the clock and beat your own best score.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mode-card">
        <div class="mode-icon">📅</div>
        <h3>Daily Word</h3>
        <p>One word per day, same for all players worldwide. Compare your solve with everyone else.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── CTA ── -->
  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to Race?</h2>
    <p>Free to play. No download. No account needed — just share a link and battle.</p>
    <a href="https://wordrace-game.netlify.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">⚡ &nbsp;Play WordRace Free</a>
    <p class="cta-url">wordrace-game.netlify.app</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
